---
description: "Pre-commit and pre-release validation for AFNM mods. Activate before committing, pushing, or claiming work is done."
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

See `docs/skills/pre-commit-validation.md`.

Before any commit: `bun run typecheck && bun run build`
Before any release: `bun run release:validate`
Before claiming a hook exists: `bun run runtime:grep -- "<hook-name>"`
Check `git diff` for secrets before committing.
Follow commit conventions: `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `perf:`, `chore:`.
